When you ask, ‚ÄúWhat should I eat right now?‚Äù ü•ò, `InvokeAgentAsync` sends your request to the Food Agent, who now has all the context to make a smart recommendation. The agent ensures all meal suggestions are halal or vegetarian üå±, and even provides the recipe to go along with the dish. The `ChatHistory` keeps track of your culinary conversation üç¥, so you can ask follow-up questions and get new suggestions. With the added plugins, the assistant is ready to guide you through tasty and thoughtful meal choices at any time!

